---
title: Hoisin Beef & Mushroom Tacos with Garlic Aioli
description: We love inventing new flavour combinations that work in tacos, and we think these Chinese takeaway inspired ones are some
of our favourites. With loads of umami from mushrooms, hoisin sauce and tender beef, plus crisp lettuce and creamy aioli,
this meal puts the fun into fusion!
